review:
Pros:
- The most refined gameplay yet;
- Challenging. Requires lots of thinking and strategies;
- Good graphics;
- Great sound design and voices;
- Good DLCs (also because of returning character which is very OP)

Cons:
- The story is non-existent;
- The dialogue is boring and beyond cringe;
- Dieversity propaganda that caused the studio to go bankrupt and shut down (lol!)
